  {
    "startTime": 674.707,
    "endTime": 680.813,
    "text": "[ Laughter ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 680.813,
    "endTime": 682.2139999999999,
    "text": "-All right, what do we got? What do we got?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 682.214,
    "endTime": 683.649,
    "text": "What are we doing? -What you got?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 683.649,
    "endTime": 685.917,
    "text": "-So, for this last animal, we're all gonna come down here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 685.917,
    "endTime": 688.186,
    "text": "We're gonna join you down here. -Well, I'mma go up here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 688.186,
    "endTime": 689.921,
    "text": "[ Laughter and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 689.921,
    "endTime": 692.758,
    "text": "I'mma go up here. -Dude, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 692.758,
    "endTime": 694.927,
    "text": "-I'mma go up here. -No, all right, come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 694.927,
    "endTime": 696.428,
    "text": "It's gonna be fine. This'll be fine, here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 696.428,
    "endTime": 698.43,
    "text": "-I don't like nothing standing behind me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 698.43,
    "endTime": 700.799,
    "text": "[ Cheers and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 700.799,
    "endTime": 702.268,
    "text": "-This one's gonna be good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 702.268,
    "endTime": 704.102,
    "text": "I promise you, this one will be awesome."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 704.102,
    "endTime": 705.7379999999999,
    "text": "-Okay. -So this one's name is --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 705.738,
    "endTime": 707.206,
    "text": "He's actually got a very cute name."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 707.206,
    "endTime": 711.343,
    "text": "It's Squire. And Squire is a falcon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 711.343,
    "endTime": 712.877,
    "text": "-A what? -He's a falcon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 712.878,
    "endTime": 714.88,
    "text": "All right, so come on out, Squire."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 714.88,
    "endTime": 715.948,
    "text": "There we go. -Come on now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 715.948,
    "endTime": 717.75,
    "text": "-He's a lanner falcon. -Come on, now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 717.75,
    "endTime": 719.117,
    "text": "-They are beautiful birds. They really are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 719.117,
    "endTime": 721.654,
    "text": "-You know what birds like? Small objects."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 721.654,
    "endTime": 723.889,
    "text": "[ Laughter ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 723.889,
    "endTime": 726.191,
    "text": "-Wow. -So, they use those feet --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 726.191,
    "endTime": 728.794,
    "text": "They've got really strong talons, those killing claws."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 728.794,
    "endTime": 730.829,
    "text": "That's what they use to actually hunt their prey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 730.829,
    "endTime": 733.4639999999999,
    "text": "They're really quick, they're keyed in to movement."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 733.465,
    "endTime": 735.567,
    "text": "So, what I want to do with this one --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 735.567,
    "endTime": 737.569,
    "text": "They're amazing at flying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 737.569,
    "endTime": 740.506,
    "text": "So I'm thinking, if you two want to go up into the audience"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 740.506,
    "endTime": 743.4,
    "text": "and we'll get this one flying to you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 743.41,
    "endTime": 748.581,
    "text": "[ Cheers and applause ] Does that sound good?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 748.581,
    "endTime": 751.16,
    "text": "What do you reckon? -Come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 751.16,
    "endTime": 754.319,
    "text": "-Okay, so -- [ Cheers and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 754.32,
    "endTime": 756.821,
    "text": "-Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 756.821,
    "endTime": 759.291,
    "text": "-No. No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 759.291,
    "endTime": 760.625,
    "text": "-You stay here, Kevin. -No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 760.625,
    "endTime": 761.893,
    "text": "-You stay here. [ Cheers and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 761.893,
    "endTime": 763.395,
    "text": "-I'll stay here. -All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 763.395,
    "endTime": 764.963,
    "text": "-I'll head up this side. -You go up that one?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 764.963,
    "endTime": 767.433,
    "text": "-You go, Jimmy. -Okay, I'll stand in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 767.433,
    "endTime": 775.107,
    "text": "[ Cheers and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 775.107,
    "endTime": 777.242,
    "text": "-Thank you. Oh, wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 777.242,
    "endTime": 779.111,
    "text": "-Gonna put it down to your side to start..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 779.111,
    "endTime": 781.346,
    "text": "-Okay. So, what we're gonna do is,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 781.346,
    "endTime": 783.448,
    "text": "I'm gonna call him over, and once he's ready,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 783.448,
    "endTime": 784.683,
    "text": "he'll fly over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 784.683,
    "endTime": 786.51,
    "text": "Make sure you don't put your hands up, though,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 786.51,
    "endTime": 787.2189999999999,
    "text": "'cause those talons are very sharp."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 787.219,
    "endTime": 789.889,
    "text": "-Oh, my God. -Kevin, don't move."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 789.889,
    "endTime": 791.323,
    "text": "Kevin, put your hands down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 791.323,
    "endTime": 794.526,
    "text": "-Jimmy, I saw this in a movie. -Kevin, put your --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 794.526,
    "endTime": 795.894,
    "text": "-That's how people die!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 795.894,
    "endTime": 798.597,
    "text": "-Aww! Awesome! How cool is that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 798.597,
    "endTime": 799.698,
    "text": "[ Cheers and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 799.698,
    "endTime": 802.668,
    "text": "-Good job. Awesome, huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 802.668,
    "endTime": 804.436,
    "text": "Okay. Jimmy, it's your turn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 804.436,
    "endTime": 807.539,
    "text": "[ Applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 807.539,
    "endTime": 809.909,
    "text": "Hey, look over there, Squire. It's Jimmy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 809.909,
    "endTime": 812.778,
    "text": "There you go. Ooh, he's on you now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 812.778,
    "endTime": 814.79,
    "text": "There we go. He's on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 814.79,
    "endTime": 815.5799999999999,
    "text": "Oh, awesome."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 815.581,
    "endTime": 817.4490000000001,
    "text": "[ Cheers and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 817.449,
    "endTime": 820.853,
    "text": "Nice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 820.853,
    "endTime": 822.9209999999999,
    "text": "-Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 822.922,
    "endTime": 824.49,
    "text": "-Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 824.49,
    "endTime": 826.992,
    "text": "So, what we're gonna do, we're gonna keep this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 826.992,
    "endTime": 831.63,
    "text": "nice and still just like that. Just like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 831.63,
    "endTime": 832.531,
    "text": "Perfect. You're good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 832.531,
    "endTime": 834.833,
    "text": "So just keep that one still. [ Laughter and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 834.833,
    "endTime": 836.535,
    "text": "-She's looking at you, Kev."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 836.535,
    "endTime": 839.504,
    "text": "She's looking at you, Kev."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 839.504,
    "endTime": 840.673,
    "text": "-All right, we ready?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 840.673,
    "endTime": 841.674,
    "text": "-Don't look at me. No, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 841.674,
    "endTime": 843.74,
    "text": "-Ready, Kevin? [ Laughter ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 843.75,
    "endTime": 844.676,
    "text": "-Look that way. -Squire."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 844.676,
    "endTime": 849.4140000000001,
    "text": "-No, look that way. [ Laughter ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 849.414,
    "endTime": 851.16,
    "text": "-What's happening, Jimmy? -Oh, here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 851.16,
    "endTime": 852.817,
    "text": "Here he goes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 852.817,
    "endTime": 855.8870000000001,
    "text": "[ Cheering and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 855.887,
    "endTime": 858.223,
    "text": "-Oh [bleep] -Yes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 858.223,
    "endTime": 860.492,
    "text": "-Oh! -Good job."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 860.492,
    "endTime": 863.5999999999999,
    "text": "-Oh! Jimmy, get it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 863.61,
    "endTime": 865.163,
    "text": "Jimmy -- Jimmy, get it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 865.163,
    "endTime": 866.564,
    "text": "-Robert Irwin, everybody!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 866.564,
    "endTime": 869.67,
    "text": "-Jimmy, get it! Jimmy, get it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 869.67,
    "endTime": 870.668,
    "text": "Jimmy, get it! -\"Crikey!\" --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 870.668,
    "endTime": 872.704,
    "text": "-Get it, Jimmy! Jimmy, get it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 872.704,
    "endTime": 875.64,
    "text": "\"Crikey! It's the Irwins\" premieres October 28th,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 875.64,
    "endTime": 877.641,
    "text": "at 8:00 p.m., on Animal Planet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 877.642,
    "endTime": 879.4300000000001,
    "text": "We'll be right back. Stick around, everybody."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 879.43,
    "endTime": 881.247,
    "text": "-Y'all got to get it, Jimmy. [ Cheers and applause ]"
  }
]